      "value": "<p>Your extensive study of religion rewards you with the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Increase your Intelligence score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li>\n<li>You double your proficiency bonus for checks you make with the Religion skill.</li>\n<li>You learn the @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.MUO1uYN7JR1hm4dR]{Thaumaturgy} and @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Mzh95utKDPIrjiH8]{Detect Evil and Good} spells. You can cast @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Mzh95utKDPIrjiH8]{Detect Evil and Good} once without expending a spell slot, and you regain the ability to do so when you finish a long rest.</li>\n</ul>",
